                                    <span style="background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem;">Enviado</span>
                                </td>
                                <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
                                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center;">
